    "description": "<p><span ><strong >Trigger:</strong></span> You are the target of an<span ><strong > Attack</strong></span>.</p><p><strong>Reaction: </strong><span >You can spend <strong >2 AP</strong></span> and <span ><strong >1 SP </strong></span>to move up to your Speed and avoid the attack entirely as long as you end your movement outside of the range or behind Full Cover of the Attack. This movement provokes <strong>Opportunity</strong> <strong>Attacks</strong> as normal.</p><p></p><p><span ><strong><span >Technique Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><ul><li><span ><strong >Heroic Dive:</strong> <strong >(2 SP)</strong></span> <span >You can bring 1 additional willing creature along with you as part of Tumble and Dive. They move the same amount of Spaces as you and must also end their movement within 1 Space of you.</span></li></ul>",
